data.description: MUST SEE! Charming 4 bed 2 bath home in a wonderful Yankee Springs neighborhood! Walking distance to Payne Lake & just a short drive to several area lakes, parks, restaurants, hiking trails, etc. Impressive covered front entry porch & large tree lined yard for a more secluded feel. Open floorplan offering a large master suite w/tub, shower & walk-in closet, huge living room w/picture window, bedroom w/built-ins currently used as family room/office, & new laminate flooring in the laundry, kitchen & dining area. All kitchen appliances, washer & dryer included. Almost half an acre of property w/paved drive, 1-stall garage & storage shed. Seller to have possession for 7 days after close. Start your Summer off right...enjoying all that this home & the Yankee Springs area has to offer!
